{"tid":135446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸妹無做功課 俾老師扭甩耳仔縫5針","createTime":"2017-02-26T11:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T12:04:20.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08a6c821ae7675c50ccda0d059b13f1739026e49","tid":135446,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T11:07:29.000Z","msg":"<strong>小二女生無做功課 俾老師扭甩耳仔縫5針</strong><br />\n<br />\n2017-02-26 17:32:53 HKT  <br />\n         <br />\n陝西商洛鎮安縣城關小學二年級6班的小褘(化名)，上周四下午上語文課時，因未完成功課，遭班主任盧付珍扭耳仔，結果導致耳朵被撕裂。小褘忍着痛楚，直到放學後被家長發現，到醫院縫了5針。<br />\n<br />\n小褘的家長，事後將孩子的遭遇在網上公開，班主任才聯絡他，表示道歉，並要求他刪掉有關網帖。而學校一直未出面解決此事。商洛市教育局已督促相關部門介入調查。"},{"pid":"5d792faaee8fa78cef829e7a7f090cf2068d7a6e","tid":135446,"uid":45138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T11:11:08.000Z","msg":"支那+教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87424a344536a9a5203795fd7ded92cd31c8956","tid":135446,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T11:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c17a4093348f171caccb503ede0177e7eeccbc","tid":135446,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T12:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果盧主任係後生女就好啦<br />\n<br />\n比五百人仔瘋玩佢耳仔"}]}